 will be located at geographically separate locations in the UK.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system will provide a further database server in the USA in order to
 facilitate disaster recovery.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Usability
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
The system shall be easy to use (as evidenced by 80% positive feedback from
 'usability' questions on user satisfaction questionnaires).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system shall provide the user with context specific help.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The system shall provide the user with information on the progress of all
 searches taking more than 3 seconds.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
